Class Cost

  • java.lang.Object
    • eventak.Cost

  • public class Cost
extends java.lang.Object
    Cost. Covers budget, etc. Made instead of using an int for budget because calculations for cost/person / estimations/etc would be needed. Has: - total: total budget - people: number of people (can also be used for any partition of things. Like number of booths, etc)
